Parliament, Wednesday, 24 October 2018 – The Joint Constitutional Review Committee will tomorrow, 25 October 2018, continue with oral submissions from various presenters on a possible review of section 25 of the Constitution. Details are as follows: 
	Date: Thursday, 25 October 2018
	Time: 10:00
	Venue: Committee Room V475, Fourth Floor, Old Assembly Building. Please find the draft agenda at:
